<br>
&quot;I can nae take all the credit for the armor I wear.  A number of friends were a great help in gathering all the needed parts from the Orcs of Crushbone.&quot;<br>
<br>
Looking at her bow, he smiles.<br>
<br>
&quot;Your Da is a skilled fletcher and bowyer indeed.  I see the gift has been passed to his daughter as well.&quot;<br>
<br>
The girl's voice lowers to a whisper as she speaks of the kobolds and their apparent collaboration with the orcs.  He leans in close to hear her words, aware that unfriendly ears in the shadows strain to hear them as well.<br>
<br>
&quot;Aye, if true, this is verra disturbing indeed.  I have just come from Crushbone and the threat there is still strong.  The last thing we need is a battle on another front.&quot;<br>
<br>
He raises an eyebrow at the lass as she speaks of her plans to descend in to the Warrens, then nods in agreement.<br>
<br>
&quot;You are quite right. Such information could prove verra useful.  It would be wise to take a trusted mate with you on such a long and dangerous journey.  And try to learn a bit of the Erudian tongue before you go....it is always good to know what others say behind your back.&quot;<br>
<br>
He pauses to finish off the mead as Lynxettia whispers in his ear.  Keirus smiles, nodding in approval at her idea, and kisses her on the cheek.<br>
<br>
&quot;Aye, love....that's a grand idea.&quot;<br>
<br>
Turning to the ranger, he winks and tells her the plan.<br>
<br>
&quot;I've an enchanter friend from Felwithe who can take on the appearance of a Gnome.  We will travel to Steamfont and convince the kobolds that they have enough trouble near Ak' Anon.  That should keep them off of us for a while.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showPrevMessage?topicID=127.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showNextMessage?topicID=127.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=127.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.threadControl?topicID=127.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=127.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm23.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=127.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub94.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="firionaviefrm1">Firiona Vie General Chat<option value="firionaviefrm9">OT/OOC Forum<option value="firionaviefrm4">The Soapbox<option value="firionaviefrm58">Telegrams!<option value="firionaviefrm47">Guilds and Associations<option value="firionaviefrm10">A Bard for a Da